title: Previewing Top Matchups for Week 8
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, and "Stanford" Steve Coughlin dive into the five week 8 ranked CFB matchups. They take deep looks into Kansas State vs TCU and Oregon vs UCLA. Additionally, Heather Dinich joins the show to discuss the College Football Playoff Expansion plans.
